    {
      "chinese": "依居住地區劃分為五個亞群：\r\n（一）南勢阿美：花蓮市、新城鄉、吉安鄉、壽豐鄉。（二）秀姑巒阿美：鳳林鎮、光復鄉、瑞穗鄉、玉里鎮、富里鄉。（三）海岸阿美：豐濱鄉、長濱鄉、成功鎮以北。（四）馬蘭阿美：成功鎮以南、東河鄉、馬蘭平原一帶等。（五）恆春阿美：鹿野鄉、關山鎮、池上鄉、屏東縣滿州鄉一部分。",
      "ab": "Ano pakayni i paniyaro’an no Pangcah i, lima^ ko kasasiroma^. Saka-cecay, o no ’amisay a Pangcah i, o Kalingko^, Singcen, Yosino^, Rinahem. Saka-tosa^,  o  no Siwkolang a Pangcah i, o Cingaloan, Fata’an, Kohkoh, Poseko^, Kongpo^. \r\n[===]Saka-tolo^, o no walian a Pangcah i, o Fakong, Kakacawan, sa’amisan no Madawdaw. Saka-sepat i, o Falangaw a Pangcah. Satimolan no Madawdaw i, o Fafokod, o enar no Falangaw. Saka-lima^ i, o Palidaw a Pangcah, o Palayapay, Kan-cang, Fanaw, Pingtongay a Palidaw.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2020/10/21/b6edc1cd1f36e45daf6d7824d7bb2283.wav",
